AID TODAY IN SAN JOSE THAT HE ASKED PRESIDENT OSCAR ARIAS TO "MEDIATE TO BRING ABOUT A SOLUTION TO THE SALVADORAN CONFLICT AND STEP UP EFFORTS TO PREVENT "MASSACRES" AND "SELECTIVE MURDERS."
